extends layout

block content
  .hero-section
    h1.hero-title Welcome to Our Business
    p.hero-subtitle Your trusted partner for professional services

  .content-section
    .container
      .row
        .col
          h2 About Us
          p We are a leading company dedicated to providing exceptional services to our clients. With years of experience in the industry, we have built a reputation for excellence and reliability.
          p Our team of professionals is committed to delivering high-quality solutions that meet your specific needs and exceed your expectations.

        .col
          h2 Why Choose Us?
          ul.features-list
            li Professional expertise and experience
            li Personalized service tailored to your needs
            li Competitive pricing and transparent billing
            li Reliable support during business hours
            li Proven track record of success

  .cta-section
    .container
      h2 Ready to Get Started?
      p Contact us today to learn more about how we can help your business succeed.
      a.btn.btn-primary(href='/contact') Get in Touch
